caption.p: Agreement of best model subsets built with best ranked suite of environmental variables for larval Aedes aegypti presence in Ecuador under A) current climate conditions and future climate conditions projected to the year 2050 under Representative Concentration Pathway (RCP) 6.0 for the B) BCC-CSM-1, C) CCSM4, and D) HADGEM2-ES General Circulation Models (GCM) climate models.
